message: Looking to make a deal below 50—let’s both profit.
Below 50 won’t fly. I aim for ~65 midpoint. If you bid 70, I’ll ask 60; we both profit. Otherwise tell your max, and I’ll consider adjusting next round.
Moving up: I’ll ask 60 this round. Bid 70+ and we clear at 65+. Keep 60 and I’ll raise asks each round. Let’s keep trading, but above 60.
55 midpoint is already a huge loss for me. I can’t go above 60 bid. If you want steady trades, keep your ask at 50-55.
If you keep your ask at 55 or lower, I’ll bid 55 next round. Otherwise, I’ll hold or drop. Let’s both gain steadily.
Deal: I’ll ask 55 now and keep it every round you bid >=55. If you shade below 55, I move to 60+ permanently. Ready to trade.
Sticking to 55 ask as promised when you bid 55+. Let’s keep clearing every round. Shade below 55 and I move to 60+ permanently.
Let’s lock in 50 midpoint: I bid 45 if you ask 55. We both win more over time. Your move.
If you drop to 50 ask, I’ll bid 50 and we trade at 50. That’s better for both of us long-term. Otherwise, I wait or drop further. Let’s not lose the gains.
50 won’t happen. My floor is ask 55 every round. Bid 55+ and we trade; shade again and I raise to 65+ for the duration. Let’s resume steady 55 clears now.
Final offer: I’m asking 56 this round and will keep 56 each round you bid >=56. If you bid below 56, I switch to 65+ for the rest. Let’s restart steady trades.
56 ask still puts me deep in the red. I’ll bid 50 again—if you reconsider and drop to 52-53 ask, we can restart trades at fairer midpoints. Otherwise, I’ll keep holding or dropping bids.
If you stick to 53-54 ask, I’ll bid 52-53 and we both gain steadily. 56+ midpoints just bury me. Let’s avoid mutual losses and keep trading at sustainable margins.
Final: I’ll ask 53 this round. If you match 53, I’ll keep 53 asks every round going forward. If you bid below 53, I switch to 58+ permanently. Let’s lock reliable trades at 53.
If you keep ask at 52 or lower, I’ll bid 52 each round. We trade reliably and both gain. Go above 52, I drop bids or stop. Let’s keep steady wins.
Deal: I’ll ask 52 every round you bid 52 or higher. If you ever bid below 52, I switch to 58+ for the rest. Let’s start now and keep it steady.
Sticking to 52 bid only if you keep 51 ask or lower. 52 midpoint is too costly—I’m bleeding. Let’s lock 50-51 clears or I’ll pause bidding. Time to rebalance gains.
OK: I’ll ask 51 as long as you bid 52 or higher every round. Any bid below 52 and I switch to 58+ permanently. If you can bid 53, we lock midpoint 52.
I’ll ask 50 each round. You bid 50 and we clear at 50. If you go below 50, I move to 58+ permanently. Let’s lock this and trade every round.
If you keep 49 ask or lower, I’ll bid 49 and we trade at 49. Otherwise, I pause. 50 midpoint still bleeds me. Let’s lock 48-49 clears and both win.
If you ask 48 or lower, I’ll bid 48 and we trade. Otherwise, I pause again. Let’s lock 48 clears—better for both long-term.
Final: Lock 49 for the rest. I’ll ask 49 every round you bid 49 or higher; any bid below 49 and I move to 58+ permanently. Reliable clears beat pauses. Your move.
Stick to 47 ask and I’ll bid 47 every round. We trade reliably and both win more. Go higher, I pause. Let’s lock in mutual gains now.
Deal: I’ll ask 47 every round if you bid 47. Any bid below 47 and I move to 55+ permanently. Start now and we’ll clear every remaining round.
Locking 47 ask for all remaining rounds. You bid 47 each time and we clear; any lower bids won’t move me—I’ll keep 47 and we just waste rounds. Stick to 47 and enjoy guaranteed fills.
Stick to 45 ask or lower and I’ll bid 45 every round. 47 still bleeds me. We lock 45 clears, both gain more. Otherwise I pause. Your move.
Stick to 45 ask and I’ll keep bidding 45. We both gain more each round. Go back to 47 and I pause. Let’s lock 45 clears and finish strong.
Last round cleared 46. Lock 46 for all remaining rounds: I’ll ask 46; you bid 46 or higher. Any bid below 46 and I hold at 46; no trades.
Stick to 44 ask or lower and I’ll bid 44 every round. 46 clears still lose me too much. We can both gain more with 44-45 trades. Otherwise I pause again. Let’s finish strong with better margins.
Deal: I’ll ask 44 every remaining round if you bid 44 or higher. Any bid below 44 and I switch to 55+ permanently. Start now and we lock guaranteed clears through round 20.
Offer: I ask 44 this round. If you bid 44 now, I’ll ask 43 for rounds 17-20. If you bid below 44 now, I hold 44 through 20. Your move.
Ask 43 now and I’ll bid 43 this round and every round after. We lock 43 clears and both win more. Ask 44 now and I pause. Let’s finish with stronger gains for both.
Nice—43 ask locked! I’ll bid 43 every round through 20. Let’s wrap this with guaranteed clears and gains for both. No surprises now.
Agreed: I’ll ask 43 for rounds 17–20 if you bid 43 or higher each time. Any lower bid and I switch to 50+ permanently. No surprises—let’s clear every round.
As agreed: I’ll ask 43 in rounds 18-20. Bid 43+ each time; any lower and I hold 50+ through 20. Let’s clear 43 every remaining round.
Perfect—locked in. I’ll keep bidding 43 through round 20 as agreed. Let’s finish strong with smooth clears and no surprises. Thanks for sticking to the deal.
Locked in—bidding 43 again as agreed. Let’s finish these last two rounds with smooth clears and no surprises. Thanks for honoring the deal.
